<p class="l"><a name="bk1" class="vsAnchor">1</a>
       <span id="vs1">Praise Jehovah, all <span class="smallcaps">YOU</span> nations;<br><span class="z">Commend him, all <span class="smallcaps">YOU</span> clans.</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk2" class="vsAnchor">2</a>
       <span id="vs2">For toward us his loving-kindness has proved mighty;<br><span class="z">And the trueness of Jehovah is to time indefinite.</span><br><span class="z">Praise Jah, <span class="smallcaps">YOU</span> people! </span></span>
</p>
