<h1>Online Bible: New World Translation of the Holy Scriptures</h1>
</noscript>
<p class="title">Psalms 120:1-7</p>
<form class="formtext">
<input type="hidden" name="chapterCount" value="150">
<input type="hidden" name="verseCount" value="7">
<p class="w">A Song of the Ascents.
</p><p class="l"><a name="bk1" class="vsAnchor">1</a>
       <span id="vs1">To Jehovah I called in the distress of mine,<br><span class="z">And he proceeded to answer me.</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk2" class="vsAnchor">2</a>
       <span id="vs2">O Jehovah, do deliver my soul from false lips,<br><span class="z">From the tricky tongue.</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk3" class="vsAnchor">3</a>
       <span id="vs3">What will one give to you, and what will one add to you,<br><span class="z">O you tricky tongue?</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk4" class="vsAnchor">4</a>
       <span id="vs4">Sharpened arrows of a mighty man,<br><span class="z">Along with burning coals of the broom trees.</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk5" class="vsAnchor">5</a>
       <span id="vs5">Woe to me, for I have resided as an alien in Me&acute;shech!<br><span class="z">I have tabernacled together with the tents of Ke&acute;dar.</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk6" class="vsAnchor">6</a>
       <span id="vs6">For too long a time my soul has tabernacled<br><span class="z">With the haters of peace.</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk7" class="vsAnchor">7</a>
       <span id="vs7">I stand for peace; but when I speak,<br><span class="z">They are for war. </span></span>
</p>
</form>

<script language="JavaScript1.2" type="text/javascript">
<!-- 
