<h1>Online Bible: New World Translation of the Holy Scriptures</h1>
</noscript>
<p class="title">Psalms 124:1-8</p>
<form class="formtext">
<input type="hidden" name="chapterCount" value="150">
<input type="hidden" name="verseCount" value="8">
<p class="w">A&nbsp;Song&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Ascents. Of&nbsp;David.
</p><p class="l"><a name="bk1" class="vsAnchor">1</a>
       <span id="vs1">“Had it not been that Jehovah proved to be for us,”<br><span class="z">Let Israel now say,</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk2" class="vsAnchor">2</a>
       <span id="vs2">“Had it not been that Jehovah proved to be for us<br><span class="z">When men rose up against us,</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk3" class="vsAnchor">3</a>
       <span id="vs3">Then they would have swallowed us up even alive,<br><span class="z">When their anger was burning against us.</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk4" class="vsAnchor">4</a>
       <span id="vs4">Then the very waters would have washed us away,<br><span class="z">The torrent itself would have passed over our soul.</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk5" class="vsAnchor">5</a>
       <span id="vs5">Then there would have passed over our soul<br><span class="z">The waters of presumptuousness.</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk6" class="vsAnchor">6</a>
       <span id="vs6">Blessed be Jehovah, who has not given us<br><span class="z">As a prey to their teeth.</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk7" class="vsAnchor">7</a>
       <span id="vs7">Our soul is like a bird that is escaped<br><span class="z">From the trap of baiters.</span><br><span class="p">The trap is broken,</span><br><span class="z">And we ourselves have escaped.</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk8" class="vsAnchor">8</a>
       <span id="vs8">Our help is in the name of Jehovah,<br><span class="z">The Maker of heaven and earth.” </span></span>
</p>
</form>

