<h1>Online Bible: New World Translation of the Holy Scriptures</h1>
</noscript>
<p class="title">Psalms 150:1-6</p>
<form class="formtext">
<input type="hidden" name="chapterCount" value="150">
<input type="hidden" name="verseCount" value="6">
<p class="l"><a name="bk1" class="vsAnchor">1</a>
       <span id="vs1">Praise Jah, <span class="smallcaps">YOU</span> people!<br><span class="z">Praise God in his holy place.</span><br><span class="z">Praise him in the expanse of his strength.</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk2" class="vsAnchor">2</a>
       <span id="vs2">Praise him for his works of mightiness.<br><span class="z">Praise him according to the abundance of his greatness.</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk3" class="vsAnchor">3</a>
       <span id="vs3">Praise him with the blowing of the horn.<br><span class="z">Praise him with the stringed instrument and the harp.</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk4" class="vsAnchor">4</a>
       <span id="vs4">Praise him with the tambourine and the circle dance.<br><span class="z">Praise him with strings and the pipe.</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk5" class="vsAnchor">5</a>
       <span id="vs5">Praise him with the cymbals of melodious sound.<br><span class="z">Praise him with the clashing cymbals.</span></span>
</p>

<p class="l"><a name="bk6" class="vsAnchor">6</a>
       <span id="vs6">Every breathing thing—let it praise Jah.<br><span class="z">Praise Jah, <span class="smallcaps">YOU</span> people! </span></span>
</p>
</form>

